snippet.title: Master Detective Archives: RAIN CODE Character Trailer - Amaterasu Corporation
snippet.description:
Master Detective Archives: RAIN CODE and Digital Deluxe Edition pre-order is available on Nintendo eShop. 

Digital Deluxe Edition includes:
Game - Master Detective Archives: RAIN CODE
Digital Art Book - The Book of Death
Digital Soundtrack - Noise of Neon
Season Pass - Four DLC with substories featuring Master Detectives
Take over 10% off with the digital pre-order! 

The digital novel How to Be a Master Detective: A Yakou Furio Case will be included in the initial prints of the physical Standard Edition and Mysteriful Limited Edition, and available as a pre-order bonus item in the standard Digital version and Digital Deluxe Edition.

Pre-order today on Nintendo eShop:
https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/master-detective-archives-rain-code-switch/

Pre-order physical Standard and Mysteriful Limited Edition:
https://www.spike-chunsoft.co.jp/raincode/en/
